entries.journal_entry_description: Pirates hired by the Hutts have invaded the lower holds! Go thin their numbers. Kill at least 10 of them.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Hutt minions have taken over one of the cargo bays on the lower level.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Lower Level
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Go to the lower cargo hold where the Hutt hirelings have taken control. Kill at least 10 of them and slow their incursion into the station.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Kill 10 Hutt Minions in Cargo Bay 2
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have weakened the Hutt minions. Take the elevator to the main level and go talk to the Security Director.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Main Level
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to the Security Director and let him know that you thinned out the Hutt ranks.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Return to the Security Director in the Close Combat Training Room
